            "title": "java易错总结",
            "date_published": "2023-03-11T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"java易错总结\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#java易错总结\">#</a> <strong>java 易错总结</strong></h1>\n<h2 id=\"1字符串\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1字符串\">#</a> 1. 字符串</h2>\n<p>String str = scanner.next ();\t接收字符串用.next () 或.nextLine ()</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>next</td>\n<td>1. 不能接收空格，只能得到不带空格的字符串<br>2. 读到有效字符后才会将空格、Tab、Enter 视为结束符</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>nextLine</td>\n<td>1. 可以接收空格，得到带空格的字符串<br>2.nextLine () 将 Enter 视为结束</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"数组\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#数组\">#</a> 数组</h2>\n<h3 id=\"定义数组\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#定义数组\">#</a> 定义数组</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> a[][] = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"title class_\">int</span> [n][n];</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n",
